Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:14.84,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:15.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:26.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:34.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:51.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:54.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:03.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:15.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,160.389)}Graveyard Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs215\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(446.167,720.389)}Kabibinga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jun, Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go into the graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:20.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Shima Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kabibinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the power of Kabibinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot afford to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do\Nwith the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We might get some use\Nout of these twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the Shocker base\Nbeneath the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.\NThe test was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it into the mold cultivator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plan was\Nto incite mass chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:25.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,by cultivating mold and\Nreleasing it into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:29.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In other words, they were planning\Nto use mold as a deadly weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabibinga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need more of your powerful mold\Nthat propagates by feeding on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue to attach\Nyour mold to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall see to it that Japan\Nfalls under Shocker's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one of me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman!\NHayato won't let me join!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you working as a\Nphotographer in a while, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of this\Nbrief peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.\NWhat's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like Shocker's\Ndue for an attack soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Taki\Nfor a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That suggests he's gotten\Na tip from the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's running\Nan investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't let this\Npeace last for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning\Nsomething, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See to it that the Kamen Rider does\Nnot catch wind of Operation: Mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.\NIt's time we took the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring in the twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabibinga, what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make\Nthem my messengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use your powerful\Nhypnosis on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now members of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You will do anything\NShocker commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!\NWe're members of Shocker now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do anything\NShocker commands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? This is the\NTachibana Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to contact me\Nthe minute he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That Taki. Going off\Nwithout so much as a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there!\NHow's everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki. You're leaving\Nus in the lurch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lead, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's time to own up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain graveyard that's\Nseen a lot of disappearances nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- A graveyard?\N- Near the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency. Please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was\Nkidnapped by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill her if\Nwe don't save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you know that\NI know about Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill\Nmy big sister Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was your sister taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mako, is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're sure?\N- I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll send her to the Racing\NClub with this box of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope those two are\Ntaking this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry too much, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shocker we're dealing\Nwith, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,\Ndid they save your big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are the nice\Nmen who went with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd be back soon\Nand I should take this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll take this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Let's all have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move please.\N- Let's all have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea.\NWhy don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed a little different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Come and save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fantastic guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The mold will absorb the moisture\Nin this cave and multiply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When it reaches her\Nfeet, it will devour her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a valuable test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The mold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The mold is gonna eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd all this fog come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You were brought here through\NDoctor Shinigami's hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that sword and stab Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:00.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,That mold will melt\Nmy body on contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:39.65,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you frightened,\Nnow that I'm Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never lose to\Nthe likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll coat all of humanity in\Nmold, and lead them to extinction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's filled with a tranquilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's hypnotized!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mold is vulnerable to oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!\NTouching that mold will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this, didn't you?\NYou filled the sweets with tranquilizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning here while the Kamen Rider still\Nlives... I should execute the lot of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabibinga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will permit you\None more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat the Kamen Rider,\Nand make Operation: Mold a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail again, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, it will be my ears\Nthat hear Rider's final scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But first,\Nthe combatants who failed must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Kabibinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I didn't even\Nrealize they were twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's stooping to exploiting\Nyoung children... it's disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have a base\Nnear the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will finish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When he passes under the bell, I will\Nblow up the belfry, and him with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the base below?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion won't be powerful\Nenough to reach that far down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take your places!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where is the\Nentrance to the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing them,\Nit'll be somewhere unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear that bell inside the\Nbase, I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here,\Nin case things go badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hayato, thrown into the\Nair by the explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,transformed using the\Nwind from the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Kabibinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you have survived that?\NYou cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was the\Nentrance to the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, mister!\NHelp me, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Too much mold...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Impudent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The mold disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, mister! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It all disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a perfect\Noutcome to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Mr. Kamen Rider go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodbye!\N- Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Which one is which?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mako and that's Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.\NThat's Mako and that's Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- See?\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly,\NI can't tell them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:01.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker even tries to corrupt even\Nthe most trivial of human happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:05.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato burns with\Nhatred for their evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't let them beat\Nyou, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:14.24,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:14.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Namekujira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:20.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker transplants a computerized brain\Ninvented by Doctor Yajima into Namekujira,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in a plot to blow up gasholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can Kamen Rider stop\Ntheir dirty plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:26.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:31.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Namekujira's\NGas Explosion Plan."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:31.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,240.389)}The Monstrous Namekujira's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:31.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,640.389)}Gas Explosion Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:40.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:04.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:07.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:11.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:15.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Graveyard Monster Kabibinga